{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "心地善良的少女与被困的守护龙第4话 暴风雨前的宁静",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "修普诺斯的动作停了下来。\\n哈尔逃走后，村落也得以解放。\\n然而守护龙希尔维亚却不知所踪，\\n疑似被哈尔作为人质囚禁。\\n关于哈尔的去向，梅露莎似乎知情……"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里是梅露莎的村落……是吗，\\n我们已经从异界空间回来了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120051_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "修普诺斯",
            "context": "咕噜呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "太好了！\\n修普诺斯的分身消失了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "真有两下子！与修普诺斯的本体交战，\\n竟然能平安无事地回来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "可是很遗憾……修普诺斯依然健在！\\n分身啊！现身吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "啧！没能彻底打倒本体吗！\\n真是难缠……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "一次不行的话，就不断挑战吧！\\n用异界碎片……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "咦！？\\n没有异界碎片了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "耗尽力量的异界碎片\\n是会消失的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哈哈哈哈！真是遗憾！\\n看来你们已经束手无策了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "修普诺斯！给可怜的叛变的王子\\n还有他的同伙最后一击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120051_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "修普诺斯",
            "context": "咕噜呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哎呀？怎么了？\\n动起来，修普诺斯！动起来啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是……\\n难道刚才的战斗削弱了它？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "看来是这样。\\n现在也许放出分身就是它的极限了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "原来如此……是这么一回事吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "那我还是先撤为妙。\\n回来吧……修普诺斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "传令给士兵们，全军撤退。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "是！遵命！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "帝国军……逃跑了。\\n难道说……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "没错！\\n是我们胜利了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "太好了，殿下……\\n嗯？你面露难色，怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "以哈尔的性格来说，\\n他应该不会轻易撤退。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "因为仰仗的棋子修普诺斯\\n派不上用场，所以胆怯了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "先不说这个……看那边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120012_01",
                "120011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "长老",
            "context": "噢，梅露莎……\\n多亏你拯救了村落！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "长老大人！各位……\\n你们没事真是太好了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "梅露莎……是啊，\\n现在就让我们先为胜利而喜悦吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢！为庆祝胜利，开个宴会吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这就是森隐族的饭菜吗！\\n哈哈哈！挺不错的嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喔，你喜欢吗？\\n好，我也要开动了～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗨，梅露莎。\\n怎么一个人在这里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "啊，尤蒂尔大人……\\n唔……我不擅长应对热闹的场面……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊，所以你才溜出来……\\n因为大家都太闹腾了嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但真的只是因为这个吗？\\n你的表情有些阴沉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "如果你有什么担心的事，就说出来吧。\\n我会尽力帮你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "尤蒂尔大人……\\n谢谢您。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我很担心希尔维亚……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "果然是因为这件事吗……\\n村落里到处都找不到她……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "嗯……我问了村落的各位，\\n只知道她忽然间就消失了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "一定是哈尔搞的鬼。\\n说不定是被转移到了隐秘场所。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为了事态紧急时能用希尔维亚当人质。\\n如果这是哈尔的杀手锏，\\n就能理解他为什么那么干脆地撤退了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "人质……是啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我们的村落……\\n还没有真正地得到解放……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊，抱、抱歉！\\n让你更不安了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "放心……我答应你，\\n一定会救出希尔维亚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "谢谢……\\n听您这样说，我安心多了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "尤蒂尔大人\\n真的很了不起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "无论多么卑鄙的对手，\\n都会堂堂正正地与其正面交锋……\\n而且直到最后也不放弃希望。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "跟我这种人截然不同……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "没有这回事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "诶！？希、希里丝！？\\n你听到我们的对话了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊，抱歉。\\n我都听到了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "因为梅露莎心事重重地\\n离开了大家，我很担心……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "先、先不管这个！\\n梅露莎的优点，我可是一清二楚哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "对谁都很温柔，\\n又贴心又可靠……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "真的很厉害啊。\\n这些都是我做不到的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "其实……我有点羡慕你。\\n想着要是我能像梅露莎一样就好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "咦！？\\n是、是这样吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯……因为我\\n大大咧咧又粗鲁……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "不顾他人的感受，\\n口无遮拦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊～这么一说\\n就更觉得自己没用了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "才、才不是呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶？梅、梅露莎！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "因为希里丝刚才说的缺点……\\n不也正是你的优点吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "无论面对谁都直言不讳，\\n真诚地说出自己的想法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我一直都……\\n希望自己也能这样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶……诶诶！？是吗！？\\n有、有点不好意思呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我、我也是……\\n彼此彼此。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_05_0069",
